{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.1","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:1","prev_osis_id":"Lev.013.059,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Loi sur la purification de la l\u00e8pre<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-32: cf. Mc 1:40-44. L\u00e9 8:22-30. (Ps 51:9. Tit 3:4-6.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.13.59","name":"L\u00e9vitique 13:59","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.13.59"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.2","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:2","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Voici quelle sera la loi sur le l\u00e9preux, pour le jour de sa purification. On l\u2019am\u00e8nera devant le sacrificateur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.3","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:3","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le sacrificateur sortira du camp, et il examinera le l\u00e9preux. Si le l\u00e9preux est gu\u00e9ri de la plaie de la l\u00e8pre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.4","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:4","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>le sacrificateur ordonnera que l\u2019on prenne, pour celui qui doit \u00eatre purifi\u00e9, deux oiseaux vivants et purs, du bois de c\u00e8dre, du cramoisi et de l\u2019hysope.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.5","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:5","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le sacrificateur ordonnera qu\u2019on \u00e9gorge l\u2019un des oiseaux sur un vase de terre, sur de l\u2019eau vive.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.6","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:6","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il prendra l\u2019oiseau vivant, le bois de c\u00e8dre, le cramoisi et l\u2019hysope; et il les trempera, avec l\u2019oiseau vivant, dans le sang de l\u2019oiseau \u00e9gorg\u00e9 sur l\u2019eau vive.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.7","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:7","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il en fera sept fois l\u2019aspersion sur celui qui doit \u00eatre purifi\u00e9 de la l\u00e8pre. Puis il le d\u00e9clarera pur, et il l\u00e2chera dans les champs l\u2019oiseau vivant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.8","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:8","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Celui qui se purifie lavera ses v\u00eatements, rasera tout son poil, et se baignera dans l\u2019eau; et il sera pur. Ensuite il pourra entrer dans le camp, mais il restera sept jours hors de sa tente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.9","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:9","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le septi\u00e8me jour, il rasera tout son poil, sa t\u00eate, sa barbe, ses sourcils, il rasera tout son poil; il lavera ses v\u00eatements, et baignera son corps dans l\u2019eau, et il sera pur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.10","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:10","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le huiti\u00e8me jour, il prendra deux agneaux sans d\u00e9faut et une brebis d\u2019un an sans d\u00e9faut, trois dixi\u00e8mes d\u2019un \u00e9pha de fleur de farine en offrande p\u00e9trie \u00e0 l\u2019huile, et un log d\u2019huile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.11","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:11","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Le sacrificateur qui fait la purification pr\u00e9sentera l\u2019homme qui se purifie et toutes ces choses devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.12","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:12","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra l\u2019un des agneaux, et il l\u2019offrira en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9, avec le log d\u2019huile; il les agitera de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.13","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:13","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il \u00e9gorgera l\u2019agneau dans le lieu o\u00f9 l\u2019on \u00e9gorge les victimes expiatoires et les holocaustes, dans le lieu saint; car, dans le sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9, comme dans le sacrifice d\u2019expiation, la victime est pour le sacrificateur; c\u2019est une chose tr\u00e8s sainte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.14","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:14","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra du sang de la victime de culpabilit\u00e9; il en mettra sur le lobe de l\u2019oreille droite de celui qui se purifie, sur le pouce de sa main droite et sur le gros orteil de son pied droit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.15","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:15","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra du log d\u2019huile, et il en versera dans le creux de sa main gauche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.16","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:16","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le sacrificateur trempera le doigt de sa main droite dans l\u2019huile qui est dans le creux de sa main gauche, et il fera avec le doigt sept fois l\u2019aspersion de l\u2019huile devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.17","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:17","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Le sacrificateur mettra de l\u2019huile qui lui reste dans la main sur le lobe de l\u2019oreille droite de celui qui se purifie, sur le pouce de sa main droite et sur le gros orteil de son pied droit, par-dessus le sang de la victime de culpabilit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.18","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:18","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le sacrificateur mettra ce qui lui reste d\u2019huile dans la main sur la t\u00eate de celui qui se purifie; et le sacrificateur fera pour lui l\u2019expiation devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.19","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:19","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Puis le sacrificateur offrira le sacrifice d\u2019expiation; et il fera l\u2019expiation pour celui qui se purifie de sa souillure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.20","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:20","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Ensuite il \u00e9gorgera l\u2019holocauste. Le sacrificateur offrira sur l\u2019autel l\u2019holocauste et l\u2019offrande; et il fera pour cet homme l\u2019expiation, et il sera pur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.21","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:21","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>S\u2019il est pauvre et que ses ressources soient insuffisantes, il prendra un seul agneau, qui sera offert en sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 agit\u00e9 de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre, et avec lequel on fera pour lui l\u2019expiation. Il prendra un seul dixi\u00e8me de fleur de farine p\u00e9trie \u00e0 l\u2019huile pour l\u2019offrande, et un log d\u2019huile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.22","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:22","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Il prendra aussi deux tourterelles ou deux jeunes pigeons, selon ses ressources, l\u2019un pour le sacrifice d\u2019expiation, l\u2019autre pour l\u2019holocauste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.23","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:23","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Le huiti\u00e8me jour, il apportera pour sa purification toutes ces choses au sacrificateur, \u00e0 l\u2019entr\u00e9e de la tente d\u2019assignation, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.24","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:24","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Le sacrificateur prendra l\u2019agneau pour le sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9, et le log d\u2019huile; et il les agitera de c\u00f4t\u00e9 et d\u2019autre devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.25","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:25","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il \u00e9gorgera l\u2019agneau du sacrifice de culpabilit\u00e9. Le sacrificateur prendra du sang de la victime de culpabilit\u00e9; il en mettra sur le lobe de l\u2019oreille droite de celui qui se purifie, sur le pouce de sa main droite et sur le gros orteil de son pied droit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.26","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:26","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le sacrificateur versera de l\u2019huile dans le creux de sa main gauche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.27","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:27","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le sacrificateur fera avec le doigt de sa main droite sept fois l\u2019aspersion de l\u2019huile qui est dans sa main gauche, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.28","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:28","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le sacrificateur mettra de l\u2019huile qui est dans sa main sur le lobe de l\u2019oreille droite de celui qui se purifie, sur le pouce de sa main droite et sur le gros orteil de son pied droit, \u00e0 la place o\u00f9 il a mis du sang de la victime de culpabilit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.29","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:29","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Le sacrificateur mettra ce qui lui reste d\u2019huile dans la main sur la t\u00eate de celui qui se purifie, afin de faire pour lui l\u2019expiation devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.30","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:30","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Puis il offrira l\u2019une des tourterelles ou l\u2019un des jeunes pigeons qu\u2019il a pu se procurer,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.31","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:31","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>l\u2019un en sacrifice d\u2019expiation, l\u2019autre en holocauste, avec l\u2019offrande; et le sacrificateur fera pour celui qui se purifie l\u2019expiation devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.32","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:32","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Telle est la loi pour la purification de celui qui a une plaie de l\u00e8pre, et dont les ressources sont insuffisantes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.33","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.33","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:33","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.034,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 33-57: cf. L\u00e9 13:47-59. (\u00c9s 32:18. Ap 18:2.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse et \u00e0 Aaron, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.34","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.34","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:34","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Lorsque vous serez entr\u00e9s dans le pays de Canaan, dont je vous donne la possession; si je mets une plaie de l\u00e8pre sur une maison du pays que vous poss\u00e9derez,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.35","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.33","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.35","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:35","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>celui \u00e0 qui appartiendra la maison ira le d\u00e9clarer au sacrificateur, et dira: J\u2019aper\u00e7ois comme une plaie dans ma maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.36","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:36","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.34","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:34","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.36","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:36","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Le sacrificateur, avant d\u2019y entrer pour examiner la plaie, ordonnera qu\u2019on vide la maison, afin que tout ce qui y est ne devienne pas impur. Apr\u00e8s cela, le sacrificateur entrera pour examiner la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.37","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:37","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.35","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:35","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.37","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:37","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Le sacrificateur examinera la plaie. S\u2019il voit qu\u2019elle offre sur les murs de la maison des cavit\u00e9s verd\u00e2tres ou rouge\u00e2tres, paraissant plus enfonc\u00e9es que le mur,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.38","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:38","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.36","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:36","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.38","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:38","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>il sortira de la maison, et, quand il sera \u00e0 la porte, il fera fermer la maison pour sept jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.39","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:39","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.37","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:37","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.39","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:39","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Le sacrificateur y retournera le septi\u00e8me jour. S\u2019il voit que la plaie s\u2019est \u00e9tendue sur les murs de la maison,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.40","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:40","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.38","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:38","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.40","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:40","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>il ordonnera qu\u2019on \u00f4te les pierres attaqu\u00e9es de la plaie, et qu\u2019on les jette hors de la ville, dans un lieu impur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.41","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:41","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.39","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:39","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.41","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:41","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Il fera r\u00e2cler tout l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de la maison; et l\u2019on jettera hors de la ville, dans un lieu impur, la poussi\u00e8re qu\u2019on aura r\u00e2cl\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.42","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:42","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.40","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:40","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.42","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:42","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>On prendra d\u2019autres pierres, que l\u2019on mettra \u00e0 la place des premi\u00e8res; et l\u2019on prendra d\u2019autre mortier, pour recr\u00e9pir la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.43","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:43","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.41","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:41","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.43","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:43","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Si la plaie revient et fait \u00e9ruption dans la maison, apr\u00e8s qu\u2019on a \u00f4t\u00e9 les pierres, r\u00e2cl\u00e9 et recr\u00e9pi la maison,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.44","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:44","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.42","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:42","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.44","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:44","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>le sacrificateur y retournera. S\u2019il voit que la plaie s\u2019est \u00e9tendue dans la maison, c\u2019est une l\u00e8pre inv\u00e9t\u00e9r\u00e9e dans la maison: elle est impure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.45","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:45","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.43","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:43","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.45","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:45","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>On abattra la maison, les pierres, le bois, et tout le mortier de la maison; et l\u2019on portera ces choses hors de la ville dans un lieu impur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.46","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:46","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.44","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:44","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.46","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:46","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Celui qui sera entr\u00e9 dans la maison pendant tout le temps qu\u2019elle \u00e9tait ferm\u00e9e sera impur jusqu\u2019au soir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.47","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:47","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.45","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:45","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.47","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:47","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Celui qui aura couch\u00e9 dans la maison lavera ses v\u00eatements. Celui qui aura mang\u00e9 dans la maison lavera aussi ses v\u00eatements.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.48","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:48","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.46","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:46","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.48","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:48","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Si le sacrificateur, qui est retourn\u00e9 dans la maison, voit que la plaie ne s\u2019est pas \u00e9tendue, apr\u00e8s que la maison a \u00e9t\u00e9 recr\u00e9pie, il d\u00e9clarera la maison pure, car la plaie est gu\u00e9rie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.49","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:49","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.47","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:47","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.49","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:49","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>Il prendra, pour purifier la maison, deux oiseaux, du bois de c\u00e8dre, du cramoisi et de l\u2019hysope.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.50","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:50","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.48","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:48","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.50","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:50","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>Il \u00e9gorgera l\u2019un des oiseaux sur un vase de terre, sur de l\u2019eau vive.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.51","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:51","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.49","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:49","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.51","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:51","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>Il prendra le bois de c\u00e8dre, l\u2019hysope, le cramoisi et l\u2019oiseau vivant; il les trempera dans le sang de l\u2019oiseau \u00e9gorg\u00e9 et dans l\u2019eau vive, et il en fera sept fois l\u2019aspersion sur la maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.52","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:52","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.50","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:50","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.52","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:52","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>Il purifiera la maison avec le sang de l\u2019oiseau, avec de l\u2019eau vive, avec l\u2019oiseau vivant, avec le bois de c\u00e8dre, l\u2019hysope et le cramoisi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.53","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:53","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.51","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:51","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.53","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:53","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.054,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>Il l\u00e2chera l\u2019oiseau vivant hors de la ville, dans les champs. C\u2019est ainsi qu\u2019il fera pour la maison l\u2019expiation, et elle sera pure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.54","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:54","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.54"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.52","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:52","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"54","lastverse":"54","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.54","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.54","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:54","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.053,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.055,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.54\" class=\"v\">54<\/sup>Telle est la loi pour toute plaie de l\u00e8pre et pour la teigne,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.55","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:55","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.55"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.53","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:53","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.53"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"55","lastverse":"55","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.55","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.55","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:55","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.054,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.056,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.55\" class=\"v\">55<\/sup>pour la l\u00e8pre des v\u00eatements et des maisons,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.56","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:56","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.56"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.54","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:54","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.54"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"56","lastverse":"56","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.56","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.14.56","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 14:56","prev_osis_id":"Lev.014.055,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.014.057,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.14.56\" class=\"v\">56<\/sup>pour les tumeurs, les dartres et les taches:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.14.57","name":"L\u00e9vitique 14:57","id